@startuml CodePuppy Component Diagram
!define component class

skinparam componentStyle uml2
skinparam linetype ortho

title Code Puppy Component Architecture & Data Flow

legend right
    |= Color |= Meaning |
    | <#E8F5E9> | Elixir Backend (Primary) |
    | <#FFEBEE> | Retiring (bd-43 migration) |
    | <#FFF3E0> | Python Shell (Thin) |
endlegend

note top of Entry
    Phase 6 Vision (2026-04-16):
    Python → Thin shell (TUI + CLI + agent loop)
    Elixir → ALL runtime operations
    Rust → Scheduled for complete retirement
end note

package "Entry Points" {
    [CLI Entry] as CLI
    [API Server] as API
    [Web Terminal] as WebTerm
}

package "Core Engine" {
    [AppRunner] as App
    [Callback System] as Callbacks
    [Config Manager] as Config
    [Plugin Loader] as Plugins
}

package "Agent Engine" {
    [BaseAgent] as Base
    [Agent Manager] as AgMgr
    [Pack Leader] as Pack
    [Agent Runtime State] as State
}

package "AI Integration" {
    [PydanticAI] as PAI
    [Model Factory] as ModelFact
    [Rate Limiter] as RateLimit
    [Token Ledger] as Tokens
}

package "Tools" {
    [File Operations] as FileOps
    [Shell Command] as Shell
    [Subagent Invoke] as Invoke
    [User Prompt] as AskUser
}

package "Elixir Runtime Backend (Phase 6)" #E8F5E9 {
    [Native Backend] as Native
    [File Service] as FileSvc
    [Parse Service] as ParseSvc
    [Scheduler] as SchedSvc
    [Elixir Control Plane] as Elixir
}

package "Retiring Rust (bd-43)" #FFEBEE {
    [Rust Core] as Rust
    [Turbo Parse] as Parse
}

package "MCP" {
    [MCP Manager] as MCPMgr
    [Circuit Breaker] as Circuit
    [Security Layer] as MCPSec
}

package "Storage" {
    [Session Storage] as SessStore
    [History Manager] as HistMgr
    [State Persistence] as Persist
}

' Data Flow
CLI --> App : command args
API --> App : HTTP request
WebTerm --> API : websocket

App --> Config : load settings
App --> Plugins : discover
App --> Callbacks : lifecycle
App --> AgMgr : get agent

Plugins --> Callbacks : register hooks

AgMgr --> Base : instantiate
AgMgr --> State : track

Base --> PAI : execute
Base --> State : read/write
Base --> Tokens : track usage
Base --> FileOps : use
Base --> Shell : use
Base --> Invoke : use
Base --> AskUser : use

PAI --> ModelFact : get model
ModelFact --> RateLimit : check

Invoke --> Pack : request slot
Pack --> Base : delegate

FileOps --> Native : route to Elixir
Shell --> Native : route to Elixir
Invoke --> Native : route to Elixir

Native --> Elixir : primary
Elixir --> FileSvc : file ops
Elixir --> ParseSvc : parsing
Elixir --> SchedSvc : scheduling

Native -.-> Rust : retiring (bd-43)
ParseSvc -.-> Parse : NIF (transitional)

FileOps --> MCPMgr : fallback
Invoke --> MCPMgr : external tools

MCPMgr --> Circuit : protected
MCPMgr --> MCPSec : validated

State --> SessStore : persist
State --> HistMgr : manage history
State --> Persist : checkpoint

@enduml
